        "subject": "LU-252 2.6.37 removes bp arg from dump_trace()",
        "message": "LU-252 2.6.37 removes bp arg from dump_trace()\n\nThe justification was that the bp argument is not necessary because the\ncombination of task and regs is sufficient to determine an appropriate\nvalue for bp.  Red Hat backported this to 2.6.32-107.el6 so it has hit\ncurrent CHAOS kernels and will show up in RHEL 6.1.\n\nSigned-off-by: Ned Bass <bass6@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I56c2a977468fbd68833135c4b1def145fcd5a369\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
